Choose names, clothes and special features. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b5/Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-2Bullet4-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-2Bullet4-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b5/Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-2Bullet4-Version-2.jpg/v4-760px-Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-2Bullet4-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

On a piece of paper or computer, put together a plan of your trilogy ideas:
Start with the first movie. You might wish to make it about the hero getting his or her super powers and having fun with them for a while until the villain shows up. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/27/Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-3Bullet1-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-3Bullet1-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/27/Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-3Bullet1-Version-2.jpg/v4-760px-Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-3Bullet1-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Second movie. This might be about the hero's personal life (love, money, violence etc.) and a character (villain) interfering with it. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/7a/Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-3Bullet2-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-3Bullet2-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/7/7a/Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-3Bullet2-Version-2.jpg/v4-760px-Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-3Bullet2-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Third movie. In this one, you will probably wish to create a climactic showdown with the toughest and most powerful villain that your superhero has to face. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c8/Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-3Bullet3-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-3Bullet3-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c8/Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-3Bullet3-Version-2.jpg/v4-760px-Create-a-Superhero-Movie-Trilogy-Step-3Bullet3-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
